# HubSpot Private App Practicum

This project was created for the **Integrating with HubSpot I: Foundations** certification using Node.js, Express, Axios, and Pug. It demonstrates how to build a CRM integration with HubSpot's API using a **private app token**.

## ğŸ’¡ Features

- Connects to HubSpot using a private app token stored in `.env`
- Lists all companies in your CRM
- Allows users to add new companies via a web form
- Uses Pug to render dynamic HTML views
- Styled with custom floating bubble animation (ğŸ‰ bonus flair!)

